Allington lock on the River Medway, Kent.

This photo was just on the edge of the phantoms range today, ideally I'd have liked to go a few meters lower but it would've activated return to home. Happy with those photo though, you can see the winter colours and slight frost on the grass where it's in the shade.

#kent #Allington #allingtonlock #dji #djiglobal #djiphantom #phantom3 #phantom3pro #phantom3professional #drones #drone #aerial #igerskent

Allington lock over the River Medway, Kent.

Don't squint too hard at the lock, there's a better photo of that coming up next. This photo shows a stretch of the River Medway, some of the M20, The Malta pub and Cobtree.

#kent #Allington #allingtonlock #dji #djiglobal #djiphantom #phantom3 #phantom3pro #phantom3professional #drones #drone #aerial #igerskent

Allington Castle, Kent.

Did some googling last night to try and find some local buildings that I didn't know of. This castle is less than 5 miles from where I've lived my entire life and I had no idea it was here!
